## Composable Style Combinations

Some styles can be meaningfully combined:

| Base Style | + Modifier | Result |
|------------|-----------|--------|
| terminal | + cyberpunk | Neon CLI aesthetic |
| swiss-minimalist | + dark | Minimal dark SaaS |
